rComments: She's a great person, very approachable and cares about her students but she sprints through her lectures and 2 hours are NOT enough for the amount of material that's covered. Need to be on top of things, 100% of the time. Every concept should be clear by the end of the 2 hours or you'll be left behind and to catch up is very difficult.
teacherRatingTags: ['Test heavy', 'Lecture heavy', "Skip class? You won't pass."]
